benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: GET /1.0/kb/accounts/{accountId}/tags - Retrieve account tags

covered: Valid Request: happy path and multiple 200 responses for GET /1.0/kb/accounts/{accountId}/tags
Empty Response: empty array when account has no tags (TC06)
Query Parameters: tests for includedDeleted, audit levels, and extra params (TC01, TC02, TC03, TC04, TC05, TC09, TC10)
Authorization: tests for missing and invalid auth tokens (TC12, TC13)
Error handling: 404 for non-existent account (TC07); 503/502 for API/downstream unavailability (TC11, TC24)
Performance/Scale: large tag sets and concurrent requests (TC16, TC17)
Security edge cases: SQL injection in accountId and XSS in audit param (TC14, TC15)
Regression and compatibility: regression scenarios and backward compatibility (TC18, TC19)
gaps: Pagination: no explicit pagination tests for large datasets
Caching behavior: no tests for ETag/Cache-Control headers
Authorization: no explicit 403 Forbidden test for insufficient permissions
Internal server errors: no explicit 500 scenario (beyond 502/503)
recommendations: Add pagination tests covering page size, page tokens, and result limits
Add tests for caching headers (ETag, Cache-Control) and cache validation
Add explicit 403 Forbidden test for insufficient permissions
Add 500 Internal Server Error test simulating internal API/db failures
